entropy.core.packers

Class SimpleBinPackingFiltering

  • java.lang.Object
    • entropy.core.packers.SimpleBinPackingFiltering

  • public final class SimpleBinPackingFiltering
extends Object
    Simplified version of PackFiltering. An assertion checks the consistency of the loads with the set model. So take care of disabling assertions when benching
    Author:
    Fabien Hermenier
    See Also:
    PackFiltering
